{
  "name": "NODE STORAGE",
  "html": "<div class=\"ns-root\" style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;width:100%;height:100%;background:#111;border:1px solid #333;border-radius:4px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;color:#555;padding:4px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #333;background:#1a1a1a;\">NODE STORAGE</div><div class=\"ns-actions\" style=\"padding:4px;display:flex;gap:4px;\"><button style=\"background:#007acc;color:#fff;border:none;padding:4px 8px;font-size:9px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;\">📂 Open</button><button style=\"background:#333;color:#fff;border:1px solid #444;padding:4px 8px;font-size:9px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;\">💾 Save</button></div><div class=\"ns-path\" style=\"font-size:8px;color:#0f0;font-family:Consolas;padding:4px 8px;word-break:break-all;background:#0a0a0a;\">/workspace</div><div class=\"ns-content\" style=\"flex:1;font-size:9px;font-family:Consolas;color:#aaa;overflow:auto;padding:8px;\"><div style=\"color:#666;\">// Nodes list</div><div style=\"color:#0af;\">└─ config.json</div><div style=\"color:#0af;\">└─ data.db</div><div style=\"color:#a80;\">└─ cache/</div></div></div>",
  "ai": "Хранилище нод. Кнопки Open/Save. Показывает путь и содержимое.",
